---
// AdmissionsProcess.astro - Componente moderno para el proceso de admisiones
---

<section id="admisiones" class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 via-green-50 to-blue-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <!-- Header de la sección -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-playfair mb-4" style="color: #5771FE;">
        Proceso de Admisiones
      </h2>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 mx-auto mb-6" style="background-color: rgb(52, 183, 13);"></div>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Información completa para formar parte del Colegio Militar General Santander. 
        Orientamos el proceso de admisiones de aspirantes a cadetes de nuestra institución educativa.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid de tarjetas -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      
      <!-- Tarjeta: Grados Disponibles -->
      <div class="admission-card bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden transform hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-500 lg:col-span-2 xl:col-span-1">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-green-600 p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path d="M10.394 2.08a1 1 0 00-.788 0l-7 3a1 1 0 000 1.84L5.25 8.051a.999.999 0 01.356-.257l4-1.714a1 1 0 11.788 1.838L7.667 9.088l1.94.831a1 1 0 00.787 0l7-3a1 1 0 000-1.838l-7-3z"></path>
                <path d="M3.31 9.397L5 10.12v4.102a8.969 8.969 0 00-1.05-.174 1 1 0 01-.89-.89 11.115 11.115 0 01.25-3.762zM9.3 16.573A9.026 9.026 0 007 14.935v-3.957l1.818.78a3 3 0 002.364 0l5.508-2.361a11.026 11.026 0 01.25 3.762 1 1 0 01-.89.89 8.968 8.968 0 00-5.35 2.524 1 1 0 01-1.4 0zM6 18a1 1 0 001-1v-2.065a8.935 8.935 0 00-2-.712V17a1 1 0 001 1z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Grados Disponibles</h3>
              <p class="text-green-100 text-sm">Niveles educativos ofrecidos</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">La Institución ofrece cupos para los siguientes grados:</p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="grade-item flex items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-green-50 hover:bg-green-100 transition-colors">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500 mr-3"></div>
              <div>
                <span class="font-semibold text-green-800">Preescolar:</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700 ml-2">Pre-jardín, Jardín, Transición</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="grade-item flex items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-blue-50 hover:bg-blue-100 transition-colors">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-blue-500 mr-3"></div>
              <div>
                <span class="font-semibold text-blue-800">Básica Primaria:</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700 ml-2">1° - 5°</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="grade-item flex items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-purple-50 hover:bg-purple-100 transition-colors">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-purple-500 mr-3"></div>
              <div>
                <span class="font-semibold text-purple-800">Básica Secundaria:</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700 ml-2">6° - 9°</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="grade-item flex items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-red-50 hover:bg-red-100 transition-colors">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500 mr-3"></div>
              <div>
                <span class="font-semibold text-red-800">Educación Media:</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700 ml-2">10° - 11°</span>
              </div>
